title: JRE REVIEW of MMA 67 with Kevin Lee
description:
Kevin Lee is a UFC fighter and has a great conversation with Joe. He talks everything from training to coaching and his recent losses. He's a great fighter and I can't wait to see him back in the octagon

 

Enjoy my review folks!
